name: Epiphone Elitist Les Paul Standard Ebony
decription: Made in the FGN factory and loaded with Gibson usa pick ups. Therefore rare guitar. you don't see them often, grab it now. This one hasn't been played at all, but came from a collector. the plastic foam still on the back and the original case, tags and case candy included. Bone nut, waxed tone pots, ebony fretboard, usb electronics and the original case. Good setup, checked by my local luthier
